      • generateSendableData

        KeySendableData generateSendableData()
        This function is used when a Cramer Shoup Public Key needs to be sent via a Channel or any other means of sending data (including serialization). It retrieves all the data needed to reconstruct this Public Key at a later time and/or in a different VM. It puts all the data in an instance of the relevant class that implements the KeySendableData interface.
        Returns:
        the KeySendableData object
